00:00:04.356 --> 00:00:10.540
THIS AMBULANCE, STAFFED BY 2 PARAMEDICS, IS WHAT THE PUBIC RECOGNIZES AS NIAGARA EMERGENCY MEDICAL SERVICES.

00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:17.600
WHEN SECONDS COUNT, PEOPLE IN NIAGARA DEPEND ON THIS CRUCIAL SERVICE TO PROVIDE HIGH QUALITY, EMERGENCY MEDICAL CARE.

00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:22.240
HOWEVER MAKING THIS HAPPEN REQUIRES MORE THAN JUST A FAST VEHICLE.

00:00:22.420 --> 00:00:27.000
AND THE SKILLED PARAMEDICS YOU SEE PROVIDING THE CARE IN NIAGARA'S COMMUNICITES EVERYDAY.

00:00:27.440 --> 00:00:35.624
A NUMBER OF ESSENTIAL COMPONENTS WORK COLLECTIVELY, DAY TO DAY TO SUPPORT THE MISSION OF EMS AS A MOBILE HEALTH CARE SERVICE.

00:00:35.624 --> 00:00:41.364
RIGHT NOW, THIS IS JUST A VEHICLE, AND IT NEEDS TO BE AN AMBULANCE, A TOOL OF THE TRADE.

00:00:41.364 --> 00:00:52.988
NIAGARA’S AMBULANCES TRAVEL OVER 1 MILLION KILOMETERS PER YEAR AND MUST BE MAINTAINED AT A HIGH LEVEL OF RELIANCE, UNDERGOING A FULL INSPECTION BY STAFF EVERY 30 DAYS.

00:00:53.005 --> 00:00:57.560
WHILE THE MAIN PURPOSE OF AN AMBULANCE IS TO SAFELY CONVEY PARAMEDICS AND THEIR PATIENTS,

00:00:57.560 --> 00:01:06.500
IT ALSO CONTAINS SOPHISTICATED MEDICAL EQUIPMENT, MEDICATIONS AND COMMUNICATIONS SYSTEMS ESSENTIAL FOR PARAMEDICS TO DO THEIR WORK.

00:01:06.500 --> 00:01:15.856
AN AMBULANCE IT ISN’T READY FOR DEPLOYMENT, UNTIL IT IS COMPLETELY FUNCTIONAL AND FULLY STOCKED FOR EVERY EVENTUALITY – ON A 24/7 BASIS.

00:01:15.856 --> 00:01:23.736
MEDICINES AND SPECIALIZED MEDICAL EQUIPMENT ARE STOCKED TO BE READILY ACCESSIBLE IN THE SAME SPOT IN EVERY AMBULANCE.

00:01:23.736 --> 00:01:32.952
THESE TIME AND TEMPERATURE SENSITIVE PHARMACEUTICALS AND SUPPLIES ARE ASSIGNED, DISTRIBUTED AND ACCOUNTED FOR WITHIN A STRICT INVENTORY MANAGEMENT SYSTEM.

00:01:32.952 --> 00:01:42.500
EMS TECHNICIANS ARE ALSO RESPONSIBLE TO ENSURE THE PREVENTITIVE MAINTEANCE AND REPAIR OF EQUIPMENT AND THE CONTROL OF INVENTORY EXPIRATION.

00:01:42.500 --> 00:01:48.988
EVEN BEING WELL STOCKED, AN AMBULANCE CAN’T GO ANYWHERE YET, NOT WOTHOUT A SECURE COMMUNICATIONS SYSTEM.

00:01:48.988 --> 00:01:56.600
STAFF INSTALL AND PROGRAM ALL THE I.T. DEVICES FUNDAMENTAL TO KEEPING VITAL COMMUNICATIONS OPEN.

00:01:56.600 --> 00:02:01.980
TECHNOLOGICAL INNOVATIONS ARE ESSENTIAL IN MAINTAINING A HIGH PERFORMANCE SYSTEM.

00:02:01.980 --> 00:02:12.216
THIS REQUIRES EXPERTISE IN DISPATCH TECHNOLOGY ADVANCEMENT, SYSTEMS IMPROVEMENTS, MOBILE AND CLINICAL TECHNOLOGY, AND DATA SYSTEMS REPORTING.

00:02:13.532 --> 00:02:20.624
NOW READY TO REACT, THE DISPATCH CENTRE RECEIVES INCOMING 911 CALLS AND SENDS OUR PARAMEDIC CREWS IN RESPONSE.

00:02:20.624 --> 00:02:30.792
EMERGENCY MEDICAL DISPATCHERS USE HIGHLY SOPHISTICATED TOOLS AND PROCEDURES TO ENSURE OUR REGION HAS THE NEEDED EMERGENCY COVERAGE OVER SUCH A LARGE GEOGRAPHIC AREA.

00:02:31.976 --> 00:02:37.172
USING AN ADVANCED TRIAGE SYSTEM, THEY DETERMINE THE PRIORITY LEVEL OF ALL CALLS,

00:02:37.172 --> 00:02:43.012
DISPATCH AMBULANCES ACCORDINGLY, AND ENSURE PARAMEDICS ARE ABLE TO GET THEIR REQUIRED  BREAKS,

00:02:43.012 --> 00:02:46.456
ALL WHILE  MAINTAINING MAXIMUM COVERAGE AT ALL TIMES.

00:02:47.540 --> 00:02:52.340
THE RESPONDING PARAMEDICS NEED TO BE EQUIPPED WITH PROPER TRAINING AND FITTED WITH THE RIGHT GEAR –

00:02:52.340 --> 00:03:01.716
EVERYTHING FROM HIGH VISIBILITY UNIFORMS TO THE SPECIFIC PERSONAL PROTECTIVE EQUIPMENT TO ADDRESS THE GROWING ISSUES OF INFECTION CONTROL.

00:03:01.716 --> 00:03:08.328
