00:03:28.832 --> 00:03:36.252
EACH AND EVERY DAY, NIAGARA EMS IS CALLED INTO MANY HIGH RISK ENVIRONMENTS WITH HIGH SPEED DELIVERY OF SERVICES.

00:03:36.252 --> 00:03:41.888
SUPERVISORY SUPPORT IS PREQUSITE TO ENSURE EFFECTIVE AND SAFE OPERATIONS.

00:03:42.380 --> 00:03:51.260
